descriptions.text:
Passionate about development and more particularly about Delphi and its derivatives (Lazarus, Free Pascal), C and Rust. Yoann Thomas is also passionate about blockchain technology and its entire ecosystem.

You can find him on his YouTube channel and follow him on GitHub.

Vous pouvez le retrouver sur sa chaîne YouTube et le suivre sur GitHub.
